description: The Food Dude has become a surfers favorite grub spot for a delicious entrée after a day of catching waves. The flavorful aromas produced by this mobile kitchen has grabbed everyone attention to head over and try a creative and artistic dish. Catch the next wave when you're out in the sun and enjoy a fine meal from the Food Dude. Try a grab and go favorite the "Cone Tacos"!
name: The Food Dude
